<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">

<head>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0px;
            padding: 0px;
        }

        body {
            font-family: "凸版文久ゴシック";
        }

        /*main-grid*/
        .main-grid {

            width: 72%;
            right: 0;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-areas:
                "header header"
                "left main"
                "footer footer";
            grid-template-columns: 0fr 10fr;
            grid-gap: 0px;
        }

        /*header*/
        header {
            background-color: #FF7E79;
            color: #594A31;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .logo-w {
            height: 3%;
            width: auto;
            top: 6px;
            left: 10px;
        }

        .logo-h {
            height: 2%;
            width: auto;
            top: 2.5px;
            right: 10px;
        }

        article {
            grid-area: main;
            /*main*/
            background-color: #ffff;
            color: #594A31;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            width: 100%
        }

        /*footer*/
        footer {
            height: 62.5px;
            grid-area: footer;
            background-color: #594A31;
            color: white;
        }


        .center {
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            width: 50em
        }

        .center h3 {
            padding-left: 10%;
            font-size: 35px;
        }

        .center p {
            padding-left: 22%;
            font-size: 20px;
        }


        .background {
            margin: 50rem;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .inner {
            text-align: left;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .background.center {
            text-align: center;
        }


        figure {
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
        }

        .figure-img {
            width: 100%;
            vertical-align: top;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        figure figcaption {
            font-size: 50px;
            color: #ffffff;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            display: flex;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .decorator {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .font-size {
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 10em;
            width: 45%;
            text-align: center;
        }


        .img-size {
            width: 50%;
        }


        /*Resources*/
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="main-grid">
        <article>
            <figure>
                <img class="figure-img" src="/assets/farmily_top.png" alt="top headder">
                <figcaption class="decorator" style="text-align: center;">Timory<br />ー定時交換日記システムー</figcaption>
            </figure>

            <div class="center">
                <div style="height:200px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
                <h3>I'll tell you about my preferences. </h3>
                <div style="height:75px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
                <p>Nobody know why my preferences are them.</p>
                <div style="height:200px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
            </div>

            <a href="#">
                <figure>

                    <img class="figure-img" src="/assets/farmily_top.png" alt="cute-cars headder">
                    <figcaption style="text-align: center;" class="decorator">cute cars</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </a>

            <div style="height:100px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>

            <a href="">
                <figure>
                    <img class="figure-img" src="/assets/farmily_top.png" alt="Zerosen-bird headder">
                    <figcaption style="text-align: center;" class="decorator">Zerosen-bird</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </a>

            <div style="height:100px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>

            <a href="">
                <figure>
                    <img class="figure-img" src="/assets/farmily_top.png" alt="others headder">
                    <figcaption style="text-align: center;" class="decorator">others</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </a>

            <div style="height:0px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>

        </article>

        <footer>
            <div class="footer-c">
                <div style="height:15px; left:10px;" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
                <span class="mgr-10">Copyright ©︎ iken, Ltd</span>
            </div>
        </footer>


    </div>

</body>

</html>
